text: SKLH Žďár nad Sázavou is a Czech ice hockey team located in Žďár nad Sázavou, currently playing in 2nd Czech Republic Hockey League, the third level of Czech ice hockey. It began play in 1939. ==External links== * Official website Category:Ice hockey teams in the Czech Republic Category:Žďár nad Sázavou District
